# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s16d_519be949:

    # "Though it’s not the first time, the excitement of sitting down in front of the sealed box of gold feels fresh and new."
    "Aunque no es la primera vez, la emoción de sentarme frente a la caja sellada de oro se siente fresca y nueva."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s16d_c335e1b9:

    # "This one feels heavier than the last one, and it rattles less. Like there’s not as much empty space."
    "Esta se siente más pesada que la anterior, y traquetea menos. Como si no hubiera tanto espacio vacío."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s16d_d0ff5abb:

    # "Without being asked, Marina retrieves the screwdriver and hammer that I’ve been using to smash the locks. She sets them down in front of me, but I offer them to her."
    "Sin que se lo pida, Marina recupera el destornillador y el martillo que he estado usando para romper los candados. Los coloca frente a mí, pero se los ofrezco."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s16d_b8bbb5d9:

    # Amber "Care to do the honors?"
    Amber "Возьмешь на себя честь?"

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s16d_0bf09d1c:

    # Marina "You sure?"
    Marina "Уверена?"

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s16d_17049644:

    # "But she takes them."
    "Y ella los toma."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s16d_0c1a45f8:

    # Amber "Yeah, why not?"
    Amber "Да, почему нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s16d_0a85e684:

    # "Her face lights up with a look of happiness that’s worth more to me than the gold."
    "Su rostro se ilumina con una mirada de felicidad que vale más para mí que el oro."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s16d_d05cd283:

    # "If I’d known it was that big a deal to her, I’d have let her do this back at Shiprock."
    "Si hubiera sabido que era tan importante para ella, la habría dejado hacer esto en Shiprock."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s16d_584ea87f:

    # "It takes her a couple tries, but she bashes the lock off without even damaging the rest of the box."
    "Le toma un par de intentos, pero rompe el candado sin siquiera dañar el resto de la caja."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s16d_f12e1eda:

    # "She looks to me to open it, but I shake my head."
    "Me mira para que la abra, pero niego con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s16d_80c8fe54:

    # Amber "Nope, that’s all you."
    Amber "Неа, все в твоих руках."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s16d_4f87b4c8:

    # "But she shakes her head too."
    "Pero ella también niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:92
translate spanish hwb_s16d_4815b353:

    # Marina "We worked together to find it, so we’ll open it together."
    Marina "Мы вместе работали, чтобы найти его, так что и откроем тоже вместе."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s16d_617f4140:

    # "And she places her hand over mine, guiding it to the lid."
    "Y coloca su mano sobre la mía, guiándola hacia la tapa."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s16d_49c90cc3:

    # Marina "Ready?"
    Marina "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s16d_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Да."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s16d_f5179086:

    # "She maneuvers my hand to flip the box open."
    "Maniobra mi mano para abrir la caja de golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s16d_6f948b72:

    # "It’s full of dull-colored nuggets, like a moldy fast food meal."
    "Está llena de pepitas de color apagado, como una comida rápida mohosa."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s16d_93e08e40:

    # "I take one out, bouncing it in my palm and feeling the heavy softness that’s almost familiar by now."
    "Saco una, la hago rebotar en mi palma y siento la suavidad pesada que ya casi me resulta familiar."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s16d_8779ac95:

    # "Then I pass it to Marina, who treats it with her usual reverence."
    "Luego se la paso a Marina, quien la trata con su reverencia habitual."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s16d_4321d0ec:

    # "She gently sets it back into the box and then smiles."
    "La coloca suavemente de vuelta en la caja y luego sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s16d_aa6bb0c6:

    # Marina "We’re pretty good at this whole treasure hunting thing, huh?"
    Marina "Мы достаточно неплохо справляемся со всей этой охотой за сокровищами, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s16d_7f1c6f0e:

    # "I shut the box and nod."
    "Cierro la caja y asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s16d.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s16d_4b828c14:

    # Amber "Yeah, we’re not bad."
    Amber "Ага, очень даже неплохо."

